Thomas Tuchel's men went on to secure qualification with two matches to spare, meaning the pressure is off for them this evening, while Albania are battling it out with Serbia for second place in the group and a spot in the play-offs. With commentary by Sam Matterface and Lee Dixon, reports from Gabriel Clarke and commentary by Sam Matterface and Lee Dixon
